{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi (to Weetu) wiꞥſch\nun Preekſchâ pataiſijs/ un wiꞥſch\nnu lizzis faſnoht/ ka wiꞥſch to\nSemmi peepilâtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kalni irr ar wiꞥſcha Ehnu\napſlahti/ un wiꞥſcha Sarri irr\nka leelt Zeedra-Rohſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch iſplattija ſawus\nSarrus lihds patt Juhrai/ un\nwiꞥſcha Spruktes lihds tai Uppet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kapehz eſſi tu tad wiꞥſch\nna Sehtu falauſijs/ ka wiſſ/\nkas to Zeeku fezzen eet/ wiꞥſchu\nplohsa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Mescha Zuhka irr\nwiꞥſchu iſrakkuſi/ un tee Lauka\nSwehri irr wiꞥſchu no ehduſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Deewu Zebâats atgreeſees jelle/ ſkattajs no Debbeſim/\nun rangi/ un peemekle ſcho Wihna-Kohſu/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Augli/ ko ta wa labba Rohka dehſtijs/ un ta Dehla labbad/ to tu ſew eſſi ſpehzinajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch irr ar Uggunt fa-\ndedsinahts un iſzirſts/ tee eet\nzaur tawu Laumaſchanu bohja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawa Rohka lai irr pahr\nto Wihru tawas labbas Rohkas/\npahr to Ziliweka Dehlu/ ko tu\nſewim eſſi ſpehzinajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad mehs no tevis ne\natlahpfim/ paturri muhs dſihwus/ tad mehs tawu Wahrdn peetanſſim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak KUNGS Deewu Zebâits! atgreeſ muhs/ leeſ ta-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta LXXXI. Dseesma.\nIrr weena jauka Pamahjiſchana/ ka teem\ndu Landim buhs toſs Leeewnu-Sweh\nar Preeku turreht/ un Deewam par t\nLabdarrischanahm/ fo wiꞥſchi dabbuiſchi\ndigi vateikt: 1. Jo kad tas lihdſchin\npeederrigu Sirbs Prahtu neirr notizzis\nDeews wiꞥſchus arridsan ar daschad\nGoddibahm peemekleis: 12.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eena Afawa Dima/preekſch ta ang\nDseedataja/ us\nGittit.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Dseedajt preezigi Deewmuhtu Stiprumam/ gawile\nJehkaba Deewam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pazelleet Dseefmas/ dohdect ſchurp Bungas/ mi\ngas Kohſies ar Sohma-Stal\nlehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Puhteet ar Trummeteſchjauna Mehnefi/ muhtu Leenu Swehtku Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas irr weens Likkureekſch Israeka/ weena Tecfa\nJehkaba Deewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch irr to par Leezikeekſch Jahſepa lizzis/ kad tasEgiptes Semmes iſgahje/weeNepaſihtama Walldu dsirdej\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "* Tu/ ka Rameschus esNastahm ativeeglinajs/ unRohkas es noPohdeim atrahwi*Kriſtus runna ſchohs Wahrdus, tohsſraeda Laudis pakuhdihaft, ka teem buhsfawas Sirbs Zeetibas atſtahtees, un wiapa to ihtenu Deewu atſ iht, ka wiꞥſch tono Egiptes iſweddis, un Tukneki ar teerunnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad tu mannis erſſch Be dah-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
